org.gephi.ranking.spi
Interface RankingBuilder

All Known Implementing Classes:
AttributeRankingBuilder, DegreeRankingBuilder, InDegreeRankingBuilder, OutDegreeRankingBuilder
public interface RankingBuilder

Ranking builder, creating Ranking instances suitable to the given RankingModel.

Implementors should add the @ServiceProvider annotation to be registered by the system.

Author:
Mathieu Bastian
